Clicks to Reduce Its Dividend Cover, Declares Additional Payment

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-10-20T06:39:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/clicks-to-reduce-its-dividend-cover-declares-additional-payment.html
Clicks Group Ltd. (CLS)  said its board has
resolved to reduce the company’s distribution cover from 2 to
1.8 times from the 2012 financial year, “which will further
enhance returns to shareholders.”  The company, which declared a final distribution of 88
cents per ordinary share, will also make an additional payment
of 12.5 cents per ordinary ‘A’ share, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  